{
  "texts": [
    "This is where the usefulness of the application of AI arises.",
    "Many studies demonstrate the superiority of AI over traditional ones.",
    "However, the question is how the massive use of information-based systems, for instance, supported by cloud services, can change the price discovery process.",
    "Unequal access to AI technology among financial actors may lead to smaller providers' limited participation, posing a concentration risk among more prominent players (Duan et al., 2019).",
    "AI, particularly in High-Frequency Trading (HFT), generally introduces greater complexity to conventional algorithmic trading, notably in highly automated markets such as equities and FX."
  ]
}